des:
Quit Smoking Timeline is the skill that explores a timeline of things to look forward to in the first 30 days after you quit smoking.

You can say:

"Alexa, open Quit Smoking Timeline"
"Alexa, start Quit Smoking Timeline"
"Alexa, launch Quit Smoking Timeline"
